title: GTA+
headline: GTA+
subtitle: This Month’s Benefits
content:
In addition to the recurring monthly GTA$500,000 deposited directly into your Maze Bank account, GTA+ Members who've signed up for this month (July 17 - August 13) will also receive:

— The Bravado Buffalo EVX (Muscle)
— 30% off Higgins Helitours
— The Blue Manor Hoodie and Shorts
— Double Rewards on Mr. Faber Work
— Light Blue Pearl Chameleon Paint
— And more

Membership automatically renews monthly, cancel anytime. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
